                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A soul slime's touch siphons away portions of a creature's soul. Its Strikes affect incorporeal creatures with the effects of a <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Ghost Touch]</em> property rune and deal @Damage[3d6[void]] damage to living creatures and @Damage[3d6[vitality]] damage to undead and other creatures with void healing.</p>"
